{"tid":181103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一年有至少20萬收入，夢想工算唔錯","createTime":"2017-03-31T11:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T11:09:48.000Z","uid":50790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e056507041e08e2c0400f640b71eb41adba7bb5","tid":181103,"uid":50790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T11:23:31.000Z","msg":"近年香港愈來愈多以外購劇集及節目為主的收費電視頻道，對配音員的需求也因此愈來愈高。<br />\n<br />\n有逾20年配音經驗的郭立文指，成為配音員的有兩大入行途徑：<br />\n<br />\n1. 投考電視台配音訓練班<br />\n<br />\n現時香港只有無綫設配音組，成員達100人，會不定期招新血，每期約取錄11至12人，完成課程後一般會獲得一紙合約，每3至5年續約一次。他也是循此途徑入行<br />\n<br />\n2. 報讀坊間的配音課程<br />\n<br />\n完成課程後，再以freelance形式接工作。<br />\n<br />\n電視台配音組 較有保障<br />\n<br />\n配音員的收入會以「show」來計算，每個「show」半小時。如果配音員配了3小時的節目，經剪接後只播放半小時，配音員就只有1個「show」的收入，以新人計即大約120至150元，不過坊間的製作公司或會向新人壓價。<br />\n<br />\n電視台配音組的收入則較有保障。郭立文解釋：<br />\n<br />\n例如合約會保證配音員一年有800個「show」，每個「show」250元，即是一年有至少20萬收入。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://topick.hket.com/article/521525/如何成為「叮噹」與「大雄」？\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F521525%2F%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E3%80%8C%E5%8F%AE%E5%99%B9%E3%80%8D%E8%88%87%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%A7%E9%9B%84%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9F&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=1fad3214\" target=\"_blank\">http://topick.hket.com/article/521525/如何成為「叮噹」與「大雄」？</a>"},{"pid":"3a31c2bab028ce1d24347db9641d0ae34334e1cf","tid":181103,"uid":50790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T11:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05abd8584d1502eda8d4728bd7a4742fad4d34aa","tid":181103,"uid":51446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T11:39:07.000Z","msg":"1個月2萬都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a476a3a6858ee3925b8a4b63cf58e929f7c7ea2d","tid":181103,"uid":50790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T11:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1個月2萬都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能做耐d經驗多左有得加掛"},{"pid":"4c8a5c4f896604a6f111033b8508278af4d4a308","tid":181103,"uid":60169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"65cd98e1258b9dcb270b3f3c7bd15213deacbab5","tid":181103,"uid":50790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:33:10.000Z","msg":"想知行情姐，原來咁垃圾"},{"pid":"b2396cf7c3cd91f25b683b237e038bf543757bb1","tid":181103,"uid":52182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T14:49:58.000Z","msg":"其實做到喵喵怪  同 多啦A夢咁  又岩自己都唔錯啦<br />\n<br />\n當然愈高愈好<br />\n<br />\n但係現實係香港大把人做自己鐘意做既野都冇呢個價"},{"pid":"bd05731bbf6d476136a87d86475b572710b049a2","tid":181103,"uid":50790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:09:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實做到喵喵怪  同 多啦A夢咁  又岩自己都唔錯啦<br />\n<br />\n當然愈高愈好<br />\n<br />\n但係現實係香港大把人做自己鐘意做既野都冇呢個價</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我見好多人想入行，想問下人工會唔會加？係咪永遠只能養自己？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}